section.def:
industry
                (行業) includes a trade, profession or
            occupation;

qualification
                (資歷) includes a recognition of the skills,
            knowledge or experience acquired by an individual;

appeal
                (上訴) means an appeal under section
            11;

appellant
                (上訴人) means an operator, assessment agency or
            granting body lodging a notice of appeal under section 11;

Chairman
                (主席) means the chairman of the Appeal Board
            appointed under section 10(2)(a);
